                    <div class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-amber-600 mr-2">‚è≥</span>
                      <div class="flex-1">
                        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-800">Pending Review</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-amber-700 mt-1">Your club request is awaiting approval from an Academic Affairs Officer.</p>
